FBIS3-19539 "drweu053_j_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Latvian Delegation Visit; Ulmanis Meets With Pope LD1703173894 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 1000 GMT 17 Mar 94 LD1703173894 Riga Radio Riga Network Language: Latvian Article Type:BFN [Text] A delegation of the Republic of Latvia, led by State President Guntis Ulmanis, is continuing its visit to Italy. At 1100 today the Latvian president met Pope John Paul II. Also this morning the delegation, led by Foreign Minister Georgs Andrejevs, met the Vatican secretary of state, Cardinal Angelo Sodano. At present, the Latvian president is holding a news conference at the Grand Hotel, and later there will be a dinner given by Italian industrialists.
